hudson.plugins.warnings.GroovyParser.name: goto-instrument --dump-c
hudson.plugins.warnings.GroovyParser.regexp: ^To dump: (goto-binaries/[^/]+/(.*/)?)[^/]+\n(\S+) (\S+) MISSING PROTOTYPE: (.*): file (.*) line (.*) function (.*)$
hudson.plugins.warnings.GroovyParser.example: To dump: goto-binaries/pkg-vx/some/file/obj.o some-package 1.v MISSING PROTOTYPE: time: file init.c line 140 function Init3Dc

hudson.plugins.warnings.GroovyParser.name: goto-cc errors
hudson.plugins.warnings.GroovyParser.regexp:
^file (.*) line (\d+): error: conflicting function declarations "(\S+)"
old definition in module (.*) file (.*) line (\d+)
.*
new definition in module (.*) file (.*) line (\d+)
.*
$
hudson.plugins.warnings.GroovyParser.example: file async.c line 61: error: conflicting function declarations "__redisAppendCommand" old definition in module hiredis file hiredis.c line 1183 signed int (struct redisContext *c, char *cmd, unsigned long int len) new definition in module async file async.c line 61 void (struct redisContext *, char *, unsigned long int)
